noVerifyTip.tip: If you cannot receive the mobile phone verification code, I suggest you do the following:
noVerifyTip.type1: 1. Check if your mobile phone is turned off or offline.
noVerifyTip.type2: 2. Check if your phone number has been entered correctly.
noVerifyTip.type3: 3. Check if your SMS with the verification code is blocked.

noLoginTip.type1: 1. Check if your username and password have been entered correctly.
noLoginTip.type2: 2. Check if your mobile phone is turned off or offline.

noRegisterTip.tip: If you cannot register, please do the following steps to solve this issue:
noRegisterTip.type1: 1. Check if your account has been registered.
noRegisterTip.type2: 2. Check if your phone number has been entered correctly.
noRegisterTip.type3: 3. Check if your SMS with the verification code is blocked.

noAccountTip.tip: If your account is lost, please do the following steps to solve this issue:
noAccountTip.type1: 1. Check if your username and password have been entered correctly.
noAccountTip.type2: 2. Check if your mobile phone is turned off or offline.

noResetPassTip.tip: If your password cannot be reset, please do the following steps to solve this issue:
noResetPassTip.type1: 1. Check if your mobile phone is turned off or offline.
noResetPassTip.type2: 2. Check if your password has been entered correctly.
